{"id":721675509,"lang":"cpp","lang_name":"C++","time":"6 months, 1 week","timestamp":1655171868,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"72 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/721675509/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Delete Operation for Two Strings","memory":"7.4 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int table[501][501];\n    int minDistance(string word1, string word2) {\n        int sz1 = word1.size(), sz2 = word2.size();\n        for(int i=1; i<=sz1; i++){\n            for(int j=1; j<=sz2; j++){\n                if(word1[i-1] == word2[j-1]){\n                    table[i][j] = table[i-1][j-1] + 1;\n                }\n                else{\n                    table[i][j] = max(table[i][j-1], table[i-1][j]);\n                }\n            }\n        }\n        return (sz1 + sz2 - 2*(table[sz1][sz2]));\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"delete-operation-for-two-strings","has_notes":false,"notes":"","topic_tags":[]}
